_:Nb61178ed6d714c88a5885dbdd3c732a7 <http://schema.org/name> "Matthew Patrick MP" .
_:Nb61178ed6d714c88a5885dbdd3c732a7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Matthew Patrick was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Northern Ireland Office on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Wirral West in July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to becoming an MP, Matthew worked in financial services and energy regulation.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"ministerial-responsibilities\">Ministerial Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead on economic growth.</li>\n  <li>Lead on public service transformation.</li>\n  <li>Support the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland in engagements with the NI Executive.</li>\n  <li>Support the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland with external affairs and engagement with stakeholders across Northern Ireland.</li>\n  <li>Support the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland on national security, legacy, and political stability as required.</li>\n  <li>Support the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland on the NIO’s parliamentary activity in the Commons.</li>\n</ul>\n" .
